body: Hi Burin, Apparently the component is importing an older version of the libraries. If you upgraded to Rhino 5 the paths might be still pointing to a directory where Rhino 5 used to be installed. Use the file attached to check the path on your system. Below is the result on my system. Updating the libraries should solve the problem. Best, Mostapha [](http://api.ning.com:80/files/eaLdH5zGUVB1mQsWCrpEsDOKrWEDmeLwzlanuWqNrvJIn6n4FNT98YcXGHfIQ83bOQNpDfa7jNJ3wrBU*iWrhjzFiKZj6-8h/pathInPython.jpg)
